sentence: how many italian restaurants are in the yolo county ?
sentence-with-vars: how many VARfood restaurants are in the VARcounty ?
sql: select count(*) from GEOGRAPHIC,RESTAURANT where GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME=RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME and RESTAURANT.FOOD_TYPE='italian' and GEOGRAPHIC.COUNTY='yolo county'
sql-with-vars: select count(*) from GEOGRAPHIC,RESTAURANT where GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME=RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME and RESTAURANT.FOOD_TYPE='VARfood' and GEOGRAPHIC.COUNTY='VARcounty'
